Subject: RE:oil leak

I had a leak on my 79 2.0 that I searched for for a long time.  Turned out 
that the hole for the thermostat pulley actually goes all the way through.  
If the thermostat system has been removed, you might look at that hold and 
the mounting holes for the thermostat bracket.
